examples.en: The senator fielded all the questions.
The shortstop fielded the ground ball.
The senator fielded the reporters' questions.
Last week she fielded two offers on her house.
The lawyer fielded all questions from the press.
The Minister fielded questions on the Middle East.

We fielded a team of highly talented basketball players.
The Buckeyes fielded a young new quarterback for the Rose Bowl.
The shortstop fielded the grounder and threw to first base for the putout.
